desc_long							评测						“Overall, this is a really smart, well presented little game for both retro fans and shmup fans alike.”9/10 – The Games Den“Pester is great for bringing the retro feel, I had so much fun playing this game”9/10 – The Overshield“Pulls you in and then chews you up along with a line from The Rock saying, “come get some” to which you will oblige.”A – Video Game Attack												关于这款游戏							Pester was released on Xbox live indies back in early 2013 and was Flump Studios first game developed for public release.A remake of one of my early C64 games, Pester is a very fast paced and busy vertical shooter.Graphically remastered with new sprite work from Dylan Barry and a thumping soundtrack from Matt Macfarland.Intense old school actionTate supportCustomisable play options, over 100 combinations of playRemastered sprite work from Dylan BarryThumping soundtrack from Matt Macfarland						
